="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">小时），观察受压部位，有压红时垫软枕，缩短翻身间隔时间。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontname="Times New Roman" fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">f</span><span fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">. 增加卧位减压措施：使用气垫床或软垫，每 </span><fixedinput FixedWidth="80" operatercreater="0" /><span fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">小时检查运行状态。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontname="Times New Roman" fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">g</span><span fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">. 骨突出处及受压部位可使用皮肤保护膜等预防。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontname="Times New Roman" fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">h</span><span fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">. 保持有效体位，半卧位不宜超过</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">30</span><span fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">°（特殊情况除外），侧身角度不超过</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">30</span><span fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">°，两腿间、足跟放置软枕等。</span><p operatercreater="0" /><span fontname="Times New Roman" fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">i</span><span fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">. 加强营养，指导患者及家属合理膳食，给予足够热量、蛋白质、维生素等饮食。</span><p operatercreater="0" /></cell></row></table><p align="2" operatercreater="0" /><span fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">备注：此表参考《基础护理学》</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">2012</span><span fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">年</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">8</span><span fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">月第</span><span fontname="Times New Roman" fontsize="10" operatercreater="0" forecolor="#000000">5</span><sp